{"tid":1423600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每個人都可以反攻政府嘅流動文宣﹗﹗","createTime":"2019-08-06T14:24:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T15:27:05.000Z","uid":229880,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0125becc2f72cabbe53bc273c43d500739d2df3b","tid":1423600,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:24:44.000Z","msg":"今日見到民間記者會覺得好鼓勵<br />\n同時，大家俾左好多意見出黎，但咁樣好可能會押唒所有壓力係佢地度&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n而明顯見到佢地出黎果三位好有疲態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因此，我地同樣作為香港人<br />\n雖然未必有佢地咁叻，但我地都可以做到反攻嘅文宣效果<br />\n而且一定可以比政府每日定時定候嘅做得更好﹗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要，我地down定一堆黑警濫權嘅影片係電話<br />\n我地可以係等車、搭地鐵時，學堆廢老開聲睇片，邊睇邊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班人一定會好奇望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後，我地就直接俾佢地睇到黑警係幾咁仆街﹗<br />\n<br />\n以下係岩岩嘅影片<br />\n深水埗黑警屈9同濫捕學生嘅片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（相信最容易激起中年人嘅同情心）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/3003685459672498/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkon9agroup%2Fpermalink%2F3003685459672498%2F&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bvz%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=de59527e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/3003685459672498/</a><br />\n警賊扔煙花落街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/posts/2370746836345459\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FChanKamShui%2Fposts%2F2370746836345459&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bvz%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=40829085\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ChanKamShui/posts/2370746836345459</a><br />\n搞記者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tszonbruce.lee/posts/10156889045718780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftszonbruce.lee%2Fposts%2F10156889045718780&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bvz%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=4e08966b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tszonbruce.lee/posts/10156889045718780</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好睇少自己，我地無輸嘅本錢，<br />\n只要不斷流動播片，文宣效果點都會俾政府記者會強﹗"},{"pid":"16495d4684680ea22789c2c213e6dee38a2cd405","tid":1423600,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed5d73afcdc47162e1b3af08b54b8e63c22750d","tid":1423600,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a424a0e52df5aa9ab1e7b7e9f34544ef6d0a0aa1","tid":1423600,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:25:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004cf93311e37f0305c33202b9dc8a82834dc271","tid":1423600,"uid":33971,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:26:05.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n睇完都好撚嬲"},{"pid":"dc3e01631e9db620c74a0d8034afa057a91bdd7b","tid":1423600,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c825464b962692